Julia Caba Alba https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julia_Caba_Alba 0 Julia Caba Alba (31 July 1912 - 14 November 1988) was a Spanish actress who appeared in more than a hundred films and television series during her career. She was a noted character actress. Her sister was the actress Irene Caba Alba.
